column2: SELECT proretset, prosrc, probin, pg_catalog.pg_get_function_arguments(oid) AS funcargs, pg_catalog.pg_get_function_identity_arguments(oid) AS funciargs, pg_catalog.pg_get_function_result(oid) AS funcresult, proiswindow, provolatile, proisstrict, prosecdef, proleakproof, proconfig, procost, prorows, (SELECT lanname FROM pg_catalog.pg_language WHERE oid = prolang) AS lanname FROM pg_catalog.pg_proc WHERE oid = &&&::pg_catalog.oid
